                <h3>
                  <a href="/article/2046702/ibm-to-acquire-endpoint-security-company-trusteer.html">
                    IBM to acquire endpoint security company Trusteer
                  </a>
                </h3>
                <p class="post-meta">
                           	7 months ago
		                	
		                		
		                		
		                			by 
                  <span itemprop="author" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person" itemscope="">
                    <a href="/author/John-Ribeiro/" itemprop="url" rel="author">
                      <span itemprop="name">
                        John Ribeiro
                      </span>
                    </a>
                  </span>
                  , IDG News Service
		                		
		                	
		                 
                </p>
                <p>
                  IBM has signed an agreement to acquire security company Trusteer, and plans to set up a cybersecurity software lab in Israel.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="excerpt">
